data.description: This is a beautiful completely remodeled family home nestled amongst the tree's on this 1.87 acre property. 4 bedroom 2 and 1/2 bath, 2.5 car garage with a new pool and separate detached office space. This home has everything you need. Lots of privacy on this large property that has a park like feel. Plenty of room for boats/RV's and other toys, no HOA to deal with. This home has been completed remodeled from top to bottom, stunning kitchen with white shaker cabinets, solid surface countertops, new appliances and lovely backsplash. The kitchen has plenty of storage with 3 pantries to store everything you need. Kitchen flows into family room with wood beams and a wood burning fireplace. Also includes a formal dinning and living rooms.... perfect for entertaining. (see more info) New luxury vinyl flooring throughout the whole house and carpet in the bedrooms to keep it cozy....with new interior and exterior paint. New roof with skylights, new electrical panel, new HVAC and new pool with paver surround. Main house is 2459 square feet and then the detached office is another 480 square feet.  Termite bond in place. Never flooded. This home is a MUST see.
